  - m_Id: 304638816411648
    m_Localized: Welcome!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 304676925857792
    m_Localized: Each crop can take a different amount of time to grow!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 304724459905024
    m_Localized: Harvest crops and add them to your inventory!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 304842370179072
    m_Localized: Harvested crops are added to your inventory as reward items!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 304898141839360
    m_Localized: Touch a tile to check its current status!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 304975103123456
    m_Localized: If your inventory is full, you might not be able to collect every
      item!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 305036323184640
    m_Localized: Build your very own farm!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 305089423073280
    m_Localized: If you are not sure what to do first, try planting a crop on an
      empty tile!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 305586037055488
    m_Localized: 'If there is existing progress data, it will be overwritten.

      If
      you want to start a new game, press the Start button below!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
